Prerequisites/Dependencies
--------------------------
babudb depends on the platform classes of the Yield application server.

- checkout yield_platform next to the babudb trunk directory
  svn checkout http://yield.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/yield_platform yield_platform

You should have the following layout now:
  dir/yield_platform/src/..
  dir/yield_platform/..
  dir/babudb/src/..
  dir/babudb/..  

Building with Visual Studio
---------------------------
Create a .sln with yield_platform.vcproj and babudb.vcproj. Compile.

Building on Linux
------------------
- build babudb from its trunk with
  scons 

- Run unit tests with
  bin/babudb_tests

